&lt;/blockquote&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;content-conclusion&quot;&gt;&lt;h2 style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;Why work for Xapo?&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Impact Globally, Work Remotely.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 500;&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Shape the Future&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 500;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;Improve lives through cutting-edge technology, work 100% remotely from anywhere in the world.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 500;&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Great work-life balance&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 500;&quot;&gt;Build amazing things with a balance of autonomy and collaborative teamwork. Set your own work schedule and make use of a flexible PTO plan when you need to recharge.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 500;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
